					<h4>Heed Your Ranger</h4>
		
		<h1>Yes, Iâ€™m Guilty of a Flagrant Camping Violation</h1>
		<h2><i></i></h2>
		<div class="text-feature_print">
							<p>By Jenny Shank, 8-22-05</p>
			
							<table width="25" align="right" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
					<tr>
